<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/2922699-genia-lukin"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1306001684i/2922699._UX100_CR0,21,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/2922699-genia-lukin">Genia Lukin</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s not meant to be explained. It&apos;s a result of interacting with a new and alien biosphere, and not knowing precisely what you&apos;re interacting with, w<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's not meant to be explained. It's a result of interacting with a new and alien biosphere, and not knowing precisely what you're interacting with, which is not an unusual situation for explorers and first-time travelers. Even on Earth, people went to a new place, caught a new and unknown disease, and died of it, and that would only be exacerbated by it being a totally different planet.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
