<span id="freeTextContainer2038694896356461265"><b>If God is anything like a middle-class white chick from the suburbs, which i admit is a long shot, it&apos;s what you do about what feel that matters.</b><br/><br/>(4.25?) This was a beautiful and heart wrenching book. The characters were attaching and you can&apos;t help but root for them... but also cry with them. An interesting take on the first contact with alien trope.</span>
